OKAY! LISTEN! To get to the settings you have to go to the play store search "koi", pick the koi app you have downloaded, push "open" then push the settings icon next to the "set wallpaper"tab. When the app crashes, reset by repeating the above steps and instead of selecting settings, select "set wallpaper" then choose "home screen" or "home screen and lock screen". Go to your home screen & it will be back on just how you had it set. Even though it crashes it saves settings(i.e. fish color&size)
